00:04:29.160 --> 00:04:33.030
The first is effective leaders.

00:04:33.030 --> 00:04:37.080
I'm guessing that all of us
here at this stage in our career

00:04:37.080 --> 00:04:40.950
have had the experience of what
it's like to work under or work

00:04:40.950 --> 00:04:43.590
with an effective leader.

00:04:43.590 --> 00:04:46.830
We probably have
even more experience

00:04:46.830 --> 00:04:49.470
of what it's like
to work with or work

00:04:49.470 --> 00:04:51.870
under an ineffective leader.

00:04:51.870 --> 00:04:53.602
And they are different.

00:04:53.602 --> 00:04:55.560
And the difference between
effective leadership

00:04:55.560 --> 00:04:59.190
and ineffective leadership
is that the effective leader,

00:04:59.190 --> 00:05:03.450
he or she, has thinking
and behaviors that

00:05:03.450 --> 00:05:06.960
cause them to be able to
create an environment, which

00:05:06.960 --> 00:05:11.610
in this world we call
culture, which is productive

00:05:11.610 --> 00:05:15.480
and engaging and
gets great work done.

00:05:15.480 --> 00:05:17.610
And we all probably
have the experience

00:05:17.610 --> 00:05:20.800
of both during our
careers at this point.

00:05:20.800 --> 00:05:23.117
So this whole idea of effective.

00:05:23.117 --> 00:05:24.700
The second word,
which is interesting,

00:05:24.700 --> 00:05:26.800
is the OS, or the
Operating System.

00:05:29.294 --> 00:05:31.710
Because effective leaders with
their thinking and behavior

00:05:31.710 --> 00:05:33.501
probably don't even
know what they're doing

00:05:33.501 --> 00:05:35.550
or how they're doing it, right?

00:05:35.550 --> 00:05:37.159
They just show up
the way they show up

00:05:37.159 --> 00:05:38.450
with the thinking and behavior.

00:05:38.450 --> 00:05:40.660
And it's underneath the surface.

00:05:40.660 --> 00:05:42.120
So the idea of an
operating system

00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:45.930
is a very good analogy
for this proposition.

00:05:45.930 --> 00:05:48.000
And actually, it was
brought to our attention

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:51.480
