00:05:56.190 --> 00:05:57.630
And they ran into a challenge.

00:05:57.630 --> 00:05:59.400
Because they said,
well, hang on a second.

00:05:59.400 --> 00:06:01.620
Where do we deploy this?

00:06:01.620 --> 00:06:04.950
Because we can see this
is so good as a basic--

00:06:04.950 --> 00:06:08.077
and they called it
our operating system.

00:06:08.077 --> 00:06:10.410
It's going to affect our teams
and make our teams better

00:06:10.410 --> 00:06:11.670
and more collaborative.

00:06:11.670 --> 00:06:14.700
It's going to affect the way we
interact with our key clients

00:06:14.700 --> 00:06:16.165
on our customer relations.

00:06:16.165 --> 00:06:17.790
It's going to help
with our innovation,

00:06:17.790 --> 00:06:20.248
because we need to be innovative
and creative in a changing

00:06:20.248 --> 00:06:21.180
environment.

00:06:21.180 --> 00:06:23.070
And it's going to help
with our efficiency

00:06:23.070 --> 00:06:25.200
and our effectiveness
by reducing down

00:06:25.200 --> 00:06:28.530
waste and increasing
speed of execution.

00:06:28.530 --> 00:06:30.120
But it's all under the surface.

00:06:30.120 --> 00:06:32.220
And we know that the value
of the operating system

00:06:32.220 --> 00:06:36.810
is that, if you've got a
robust operating system, then

00:06:36.810 --> 00:06:39.510
you can run more
programs simultaneously.

00:06:39.510 --> 00:06:42.780
You've got higher efficiency and
higher speed with your process.

00:06:42.780 --> 00:06:47.910
And you get less blue screens
of death, which in leadership

00:06:47.910 --> 00:06:51.330
terms is pretty invaluable.

00:06:51.330 --> 00:06:55.270
So what we did was, over
the last four or five years,

00:06:55.270 --> 00:06:57.060
we've managed to
codify and build

00:06:57.060 --> 00:07:00.330
the evidence for what is
the operating system that

00:07:00.330 --> 00:07:03.870
differentiates effective leaders
from ineffective leaders.

00:07:03.870 --> 00:07:06.580
And that's what
GreenLine has become.

00:07:06.580 --> 00:07:08.580
And one of the other
